formattedAddress: G Floor, Menara Tan & Tan (207, Jalan Tun Razak)

tip.text: Premium spaghetti are awesome! Had to share as the portion is bigggg. Get 15% off any dessert if you order premium spaghetti. Waffles are yummy!
First try was in Singapore and now they're in KL! As usual, their yogurt ice cream is the best! Personally loved the rafallao sauce which is actually white chocolate with coconut and some biscotti! 👍

formattedAddress: Pavilion Kuala Lumpur (Lot P1.23.00, Level 1), Jalan Bukit Bintang
location.address: Pavilion Kuala Lumpur (Lot P1.23.00, Level 1), Jalan Bukit Bintang

tip.text: A minimalist cafe where they focus on black and white colours, which is a trend now. Coffee here are good, not too acidic but maybe the barista should improve on their coffee art. Overall it's good.
Always willing to travel far to enjoy their porridge and noodles here! The queue is always long.. So make sure to give your name to the boy in charge for the queue and waitttttttttt for your turn! 😂

venue.name: Pan Heong Restoran (品香食家小馆)

tip.text: Awesome coffee and cakes! A little pricey for their coffee. Interior is a little bit rundown as their walls are not painted well. Albeit these little flaws,everything else is perfect! 👍🏻
One of the best Italian fine dining restaurant I've ever been to. Awesome service, and they serve yummy sangria! Carbonara is also 👍🏻

formattedAddress: 55100 Kuala Lumpur City Center, Kuala Lumpur

tip.text: Brunch as usual, awesome. Strongly recommend their Benedict's egg! Their hollandaise sauce is 👍🏻

formattedAddress: G Floor, Menara Tan & Tan (207, Jalan Tun Razak)

tip.text: Tried out the Miss Pinky "rose mini pancakes with raspberry ice cream" and Banana choc Toast. Both were awesomely good especially the rose pancakes! Banana choc toast is a little sweet. Overall, good!
Ate the set lunch for carbonara spaghetti for RM15, excl. tax. Comes with mushroom soup and Ice Lemon tea. Very generous on the mushroom soup as its a fairly big portion. Spaghetti is a little salty.
Free flow of meat and seafood! Just order using a form on the table. Also have other food provided at the bar! 👍🏻 awesome food here, but no free flow of drinks. Meat and seafood are super fresh! ❤️
